{"tid":709224,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"唔笑似栢芝　一笑似君如　大眼氣質美女示範爆牙毀臉","createTime":"2018-06-19T23:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T01:34:21.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fbc9cdd50939b0a7a3f9d98f918042666491365d","tid":709224,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T23:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551920/org/01201482d538921b66f7882be948af59.jpg/DivloThqEU5k_BXaSzuYPsSXJ0pINyQ6GXoGWBl6Blg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551920%2Forg%2F01201482d538921b66f7882be948af59.jpg%2FDivloThqEU5k_BXaSzuYPsSXJ0pINyQ6GXoGWBl6Blg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=09d1534c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「唔笑似張栢芝、一笑似吳君如」，人的樣子可以如此神奇？五官是一個整體，隨時一個部位可以救一張臉，但一個部份亦可以導致「毀容」。內地近日流傳一段影片，只見一名長相清秀的大眼妹，用頭髮遮住嘴巴，不過當她放下頭髮，笑起來時露出哨牙，就即時讓人夢想幻滅。不過有網民認為她是「潛力股」，只要矯正牙齒就能變大美女。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551528/org/bdecc5c1a9ecb9a888cf4740efae86c4.jpg/6rS-CXD8Xjkx1E-4PUU07UonnXHEQbSIz-zQss_s0LI?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551528%2Forg%2Fbdecc5c1a9ecb9a888cf4740efae86c4.jpg%2F6rS-CXD8Xjkx1E-4PUU07UonnXHEQbSIz-zQss_s0LI%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=efb3a403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子有一對大眼，鼻子高高也算精緻，樣子有氣質又甜美。（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551531/org/cb07a8b7e2296b8f107fbe7f3ce473ea.jpg/LH6-bw6Kqqn8ZF4hXJHQZ3Ai3vN8ZGoegVskuIFbJLg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551531%2Forg%2Fcb07a8b7e2296b8f107fbe7f3ce473ea.jpg%2FLH6-bw6Kqqn8ZF4hXJHQZ3Ai3vN8ZGoegVskuIFbJLg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9216c5fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551533/org/ffaf801da93fe13ff32e0add2f672564.jpg/og59xXcorkoL9XrG_w-l0oeNihq-iVkeHCWS6hwlkuo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551533%2Forg%2Fffaf801da93fe13ff32e0add2f672564.jpg%2Fog59xXcorkoL9XrG_w-l0oeNihq-iVkeHCWS6hwlkuo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7c2dcd52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551532/org/811a798854a14d4efc3d4e0dd77803da.jpg/lFdaztq2REKt9QaA3kun9lbwpXtEpPOCKAfQhygH0Ic?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551532%2Forg%2F811a798854a14d4efc3d4e0dd77803da.jpg%2FlFdaztq2REKt9QaA3kun9lbwpXtEpPOCKAfQhygH0Ic%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c90d00fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551534/org/4daf96e24d6784097f76c20d9f7fb1dc.jpg/PBHJP_1ci2DNUW6fqvCdJZbjwCCmdXiFIunT1yLp09c?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551534%2Forg%2F4daf96e24d6784097f76c20d9f7fb1dc.jpg%2FPBHJP_1ci2DNUW6fqvCdJZbjwCCmdXiFIunT1yLp09c%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9124b1c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551535/org/4a9e7265dfbf51e92e0ee2d05d11dcf8.jpg/kvEtninF1zmS0EySbc5LdPJ37fQeVEkI2NyyWtjcslo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551535%2Forg%2F4a9e7265dfbf51e92e0ee2d05d11dcf8.jpg%2FkvEtninF1zmS0EySbc5LdPJ37fQeVEkI2NyyWtjcslo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=262c14b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影片在微博流傳，該女子有一對大眼睛，鼻子高高也算精緻，樣子有氣質又甜美，讓不少人都想博她紅顏一笑。她先以髮尾遮住嘴巴，向鏡頭表示「告訴你們什麼叫一口牙毀了整張臉」，再將鏡頭拉近眼睛，說「先看看我的雙眼皮，還行吧？鼻子也還可以，臉型也ok呀，就是這一笑&hellip;&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\n她隨即放下頭髮，咧嘴一笑，曬出一棚哨牙，原來女子前面兩隻門牙如兔子的牙般突出，將旁邊的牙齒擠成一團，跟其他精緻五官比起來，的確遜色很多，本來的氣質也頓時蕩然無存。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551530/org/ef248fa37b1dea0366ed54d60afc14d2.jpg/Zvr8q8C2t1a8E2ZMkpaRNociWSB72EeH5YsE0OWLBNA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551530%2Forg%2Fef248fa37b1dea0366ed54d60afc14d2.jpg%2FZvr8q8C2t1a8E2ZMkpaRNociWSB72EeH5YsE0OWLBNA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=363f2915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來女子有一口的哨牙，前面兩隻門牙十分突出。（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551538/org/19e0a9fb5271b771c6992fbf5f75c6be.jpg/SwtHhtUeXDkMzbBMmgye2avA1de-GnlXOQiRgDkIkYA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551538%2Forg%2F19e0a9fb5271b771c6992fbf5f75c6be.jpg%2FSwtHhtUeXDkMzbBMmgye2avA1de-GnlXOQiRgDkIkYA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=779ab33c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551539/org/45ff9dc94cb85001e4a812bd153be76e.jpg/aKoO2ogZDcJd2rKa0B-xuipMO9GwgQq7s5BOmrOQTpo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551539%2Forg%2F45ff9dc94cb85001e4a812bd153be76e.jpg%2FaKoO2ogZDcJd2rKa0B-xuipMO9GwgQq7s5BOmrOQTpo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c8748551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551542/org/3168aca78a0bcae67ad73f33f124ebad.jpg/dpBaBt0gKHK7ORQT6hjHSfvkv3Ypq2r8XFa1HFxWtRw?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551542%2Forg%2F3168aca78a0bcae67ad73f33f124ebad.jpg%2FdpBaBt0gKHK7ORQT6hjHSfvkv3Ypq2r8XFa1HFxWtRw%3Fv%3Dw960&h=65a15d42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551541/org/3ce3b02d379067f5c666be953dbaa57c.jpg/dmb0hK3RPIM_5AKlGaTSTxEpJkt_FuoNgLTWNoC01jY?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551541%2Forg%2F3ce3b02d379067f5c666be953dbaa57c.jpg%2Fdmb0hK3RPIM_5AKlGaTSTxEpJkt_FuoNgLTWNoC01jY%3Fv%3Dw960&h=df5d9b12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551544/org/5a9b3fc121118612c64a2682b0320ebe.jpg/yqfW7j2Mvey_HydyGMiKT2vjVdFAtRCKeZZb2XmWW9k?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551544%2Forg%2F5a9b3fc121118612c64a2682b0320ebe.jpg%2FyqfW7j2Mvey_HydyGMiKT2vjVdFAtRCKeZZb2XmWW9k%3Fv%3Dw960&h=34b38800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551540/org/f4585b05836febb3bbd0781f5e860124.jpg/p93eOa7Ec4FtuhxeqAnnzyb6kAHpH8ZKaYffT2mH308?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551540%2Forg%2Ff4585b05836febb3bbd0781f5e860124.jpg%2Fp93eOa7Ec4FtuhxeqAnnzyb6kAHpH8ZKaYffT2mH308%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=da7151f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551545/org/d02123cddf3a94ef4db89577e2d026e9.jpg/S4G5EGWc9leIiv6s_C9h94Tu1RKdHyUeg11LB4NdSwc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551545%2Forg%2Fd02123cddf3a94ef4db89577e2d026e9.jpg%2FS4G5EGWc9leIiv6s_C9h94Tu1RKdHyUeg11LB4NdSwc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=28f03e34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551543/org/b876e35a71667bd83176c1e89e9c91bf.jpg/lAehYfwVm-EbUteWYqMhZmj0oIPrKZ8bVllL8lZZS_I?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551543%2Forg%2Fb876e35a71667bd83176c1e89e9c91bf.jpg%2FlAehYfwVm-EbUteWYqMhZmj0oIPrKZ8bVllL8lZZS_I%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7f119589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551546/org/86801bb872749d65a82f676bb548b519.jpg/0B6rKT5LJyBdLNgI5uanc-_2MusSRUriJpZK0yaWStM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551546%2Forg%2F86801bb872749d65a82f676bb548b519.jpg%2F0B6rKT5LJyBdLNgI5uanc-_2MusSRUriJpZK0yaWStM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=70c2092c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551547/org/b9fb3296854dc25e398a13f8b79f9e4e.jpg/AwIoOYtCZG5weOjgalFdTRP2g86muDJVBP8DkQT_A5E?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551547%2Forg%2Fb9fb3296854dc25e398a13f8b79f9e4e.jpg%2FAwIoOYtCZG5weOjgalFdTRP2g86muDJVBP8DkQT_A5E%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7e93d083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551548/org/0b362f1305b35264fe311546c11ded6a.jpg/C5LUl745YpV16EZhSwAxc8oM7hf0dPl7moMuD5qDLg8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551548%2Forg%2F0b362f1305b35264fe311546c11ded6a.jpg%2FC5LUl745YpV16EZhSwAxc8oM7hf0dPl7moMuD5qDLg8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d267e57c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影片引來網民熱論，有人表示被嚇到，稱「我以為她開玩笑，沒想到是認真的」、「既以容顏得天下，何苦一笑亂芳華」、「不露牙的時候像張栢芝，漏出牙的時候像吳君如」，更有人拿她與電影《食神》中莫文蔚扮演「雙刀火雞姐」相比。不少人則建議女子去箍牙，「去整完牙真的美死了」、「不僅要做牙齒矯正，關鍵是正頜手術」。不過，亦有網民質疑兩顆門牙是假的。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：向樂高<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/200282/%E7%AC%91%E4%B8%8D%E9%9C%B2%E9%BD%92-%E5%94%94%E7%AC%91%E4%BC%BC%E6%A0%A2%E8%8A%9D-%E4%B8%80%E7%AC%91%E4%BC%BC%E5%90%9B%E5%A6%82-%E5%A4%A7%E7%9C%BC%E6%B0%A3%E8%B3%AA%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84%E7%88%86%E7%89%99%E6%AF%80%E8%87%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F200282%2F%25E7%25AC%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%259C%25B2%25E9%25BD%2592-%25E5%2594%2594%25E7%25AC%2591%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E6%25A0%25A2%25E8%258A%259D-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25AC%2591%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A6%2582-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%259C%25BC%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E7%25AF%2584%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2589%2599%25E6%25AF%2580%25E8%2587%2589&d=hQMk2f7R7Yusp0avwlpm65ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=516e4421\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/200282/%E7%AC%91%E4%B8%8D%E9%9C%B2%E9%BD%92-%E5%94%94%E7%AC%91%E4%BC%BC%E6%A0%A2%E8%8A%9D-%E4%B8%80%E7%AC%91%E4%BC%BC%E5%90%9B%E5%A6%82-%E5%A4%A7%E7%9C%BC%E6%B0%A3%E8%B3%AA%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84%E7%88%86%E7%89%99%E6%AF%80%E8%87%89</a>"},{"pid":"3e687d1b37e88c7793f35464a2e15e6c59babc5d","tid":709224,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T23:54:58.000Z","msg":"有錢整雙眼皮整個鼻 都冇錢整棚牙？"},{"pid":"3563fe0fdef6e6